285
00:09:15,431 --> 00:09:19,685
A simple man with simple goals
and simple problems?

286
00:09:19,768 --> 00:09:22,813
You can just blend in and
live the simple life.

287
00:09:22,896 --> 00:09:25,524
Yeah --
blend in.

288
00:09:25,607 --> 00:09:28,027
You know,
maybe I'll be Davey --

289
00:09:28,110 --> 00:09:30,946
just one more time.

290
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:33,866
One more time.

291
00:09:33,949 --> 00:09:34,783
Come on, man!

292
